 happier with the product.  I think it has been a welcome upgrade from Peachtree and thanks to its integration with other products really brings my business into a 360-view.  I know immediately how well things are doing, what my customers are up to, and what needs my attention.  If you own a small business then do yourself a favor and give this a try.  I think you will be pleasantly surprised.	1
