ool  Negatives to the Rosetta Stone -   - Well it is not cheap   - You must "Want" to learn the language - not partial efforts will be effective   - one license means one computer - if you have the need to run the software on an additional computer you will need to buy ANOTHER copy of the software.    Final verdict - if you are serious about learning spanish The Rosetta Stone will be the perfect investment for you. 5 stars	1
