ew other people who do so I can bludgeon them with my efforts but for those who don't have someone to practice with, it makes it difficult.  I know someone who has the Korean version of this and he likes it very much (and he has a Korean wife so he gets a lot of free help!).  Overall, I rate this as a very good package for those who want to learn the language. The lessons are clear and understandable, and flow from one to the other in a sensible and logical way. I would certainly recommend it.	1
