s regularly get 100% of viruses facing it. Generally, Bitdefender failed by misidentifying things as viruses which were not in the tests that I read.  Based on the laboratory tests and my past success with Symantec, I will be keeping Norton on my personal computers but will probably recommend Bitdefender as a low-cost alternative for family members who are at low virus risk.	1
