e because I didn't notice it while AVG was installed. The 2 stars rating (means "I don't like it" and in this case "I don't need it") is justified because, in my view, paying for an AVG one-year license can't be justified.  ___________________________________________  SPECS  System requirements - minimum requirements with 'recommended' requirements within ()  - Pentium 1.5 (1.8) GHz - RAM: 512 MB - HDD space: 390 (510) MB  Compatible with:  - MS Windows XP - MS Vista (32/64 bit) - MS Windows 7 (32/64 bit)	-1
